description: 100 pouches Parking Permit size 4 x 4 hot 5 mil laminating pouches with a clear glossy finish and standard 1/8" radius rounded corners. 5 mils (metric 125 microns) thick on each flap adds a total of 10 mils to your paper sheet. 4x4 (metric 102mm x 102mm) laminator supplies for paper lamination and protection.

Industry standard specification for 5 mil laminating pouches is 5 mils on each flap for a total of 10 mils added to your paper sheet. Also, 1 mil equals 1/1000th of an inch (or 25 microns metric). The industry calls these laminating pouches when they are sealed on only one edge instead of three. They should be called laminating folders.

Note: All laminating pouches are NOT the same, especially in clarity and bonding. Insist on authentic LAM-IT-All trademarked laminating pouches bearing our red, white and blue label. Accept nothing less.
